Detailed Description

Contains all definitions exposed by ADL for Linux and Windows(XP, Vista and above); 32bit and 64bit platforms.
Included in ADL SDK.

This file contains all definitions used by ADL. The ADL definitions include the following:

  • ADL error codes
  • Enumerations for the ADLDisplayInfo structure
  • Maximum limits
